headlines.description: Eberechi Eze's fine late winner earned Crystal Palace a 2-1 comeback victory over Leeds United in the Premier League on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Eze strikes late as Palace beat Leeds

headlines.description: — Gianluca Scamacca scored a brilliant but contentious goal to help West Ham make it three victories in a week by beating Fulham 3-1 in the Premier League on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Scamacca's contentious goal helps West Ham beat Fulham 3-1

headlines.description: Arsenal continued their blistering start to the season with a crucial 3-2 victory against Liverpool to return to the top of the Premier League.
headlines.shortLinkText: Arsenal go top of Prem with win over Liverpool

headlines.description: — Cristiano Ronaldo scored the 700th club goal of his career to earn Manchester United a 2-1 victory at Everton that moved his team a point off the Premier League's top four on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ronaldo's landmark goal earns Man United 2-1 win at Everton
